<br>
Discipline-like ability with 3 options on triggering:<br>
<br>
Focus of Flame <br>
2-5% bonus fire damage, neg5-20 fire resist, duration 15mins, reuse 20mins<br>
<br>
Focus of Ice<br>
2-5% bonus cold damage, neg5-20 cold resist, duration 15mins, reuse 20mins<br>
<br>
Focus of Magic<br>
2-5% bonus magic damage, neg5-20 magic resist, duration 15mins, reuse 20mins<br>
<br>
AA Cost 4, 6, 9 for (2%, -5), (3%, -12), (5%, -20)<br>
<br>
This would give you a small boost to your desired element, perhaps the reuse should be increased to make it a more strategic option, or alternatively a penalty to the other 2 elements and the indicated shorter reuse time.<br>
<br>
Whadda ya think? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42860">Fydar F'zlar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
